{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"title","type":"text","x":0,"y":-440,"width":640,"height":120,"text":"# How this vault works\n\nEight folders. Material always flows **downward**."},
		{"id":"inbox","type":"text","x":0,"y":-260,"width":640,"height":110,"color":"1","text":"## 01_inbox — INPUT\nRaw material. A **buffer, never a storage**.\nEmpty after every ingest."},
		{"id":"projects","type":"text","x":-20,"y":-80,"width":300,"height":140,"color":"2","text":"## 02_projects\nCONTEXT — work that **ends**.\n\nOne folder each.\nOverview + tasks + decisions."},
		{"id":"areas","type":"text","x":360,"y":-80,"width":300,"height":140,"color":"2","text":"## 03_areas\nCONTEXT — work that **never ends**.\n\nSupport, review, team.\nNo finish line."},
		{"id":"knowledge","type":"text","x":0,"y":140,"width":640,"height":130,"color":"4","text":"## 04_knowledge — MEMORY\nThe permanent wiki. Where things **compound**.\n\n`it/` · `people/` · `company/` · `references/`"},
		{"id":"daily","type":"text","x":770,"y":-80,"width":340,"height":140,"color":"5","text":"## 05_daily_notes\nLOG — what happened, day by day.\n\nRuns **alongside** everything.\nWeekly reports are built from it."},
		{"id":"archive","type":"text","x":0,"y":350,"width":640,"height":120,"color":"6","text":"## 06_archive — RESTING\nFinished projects, old daily notes.\n\n**Never deleted.** The decisions outlive the project."},
		{"id":"system","type":"text","x":-580,"y":-80,"width":440,"height":350,"color":"3","text":"## 00_system — STEERING\n\nSits outside the flow and governs all of it.\n\n- `CLAUDE.md` (vault root)\n- `conventions/` — the five rules\n- `templates/` — decided once, not every time\n- `claude_memory/` — behaviour, never facts\n- `log.md` — every input, one line\n- `my_tasks.md` — a query, stores nothing"},
		{"id":"private","type":"text","x":770,"y":140,"width":340,"height":130,"color":"1","text":"## 07_private\nOutside the flow.\n\n**Not in git.** Fails closed:\nif unsure, it goes here."},
		{"id":"note","type":"text","x":770,"y":350,"width":340,"height":120,"text":"**The rule that makes it work:**\n\nNothing stays where it landed.\nAn inbox with five things in it\nwas not processed."}
	],
	"edges":[
		{"id":"e1","fromNode":"title","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"inbox","toSide":"top"},
		{"id":"e2","fromNode":"inbox","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"projects","toSide":"top","label":"has an end"},
